{"id": 5336, "title": "Ticket #5336: Have ubertickets age out or get cleaned up on the SchedD side.", "description": "<blockquote>\nWhen a user is no longer running or submitting jobs, their uberticket and other credentials should be cleaned up.  I'm proposing a \"mark and sweep\" approach.  When the schedd notices the last job for a user leave the queue, it signals the CredD (either directly via a daemoncore command, or indirectly by dropping a .flag file in the SEC_CRED_DIR) and the CredD is the responsible for cleaning up the marked files after X minutes.  Anytime a new credential is stored, existing marks are removed.</blockquote>", "remarks": "<blockquote>\n</blockquote>", "derived_tickets": "", "attachments": "", "check_ins": "<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody><tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">2015-Oct-24 11:16</td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon dot\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\"> \nCheck-in <span class=\"chng\"><a href=\"chngview?cn=46101\">[46101]</a></span>: Create \"mark\" file when a user no longer has jobs in the queue <span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"/tickets?ticket=5336\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('5336'); return false;\" title=\"Have ubertickets age out or get cleaned up on the SchedD side.\">#5336</a></span>  (By zmiller )</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">2015-Oct-23 21:08</td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon dot\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\"> \nCheck-in <span class=\"chng\"><a href=\"chngview?cn=46100\">[46100]</a></span>: Consolidate code for clearing \"mark\" files. <span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"/tickets?ticket=5336\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('5336'); return false;\" title=\"Have ubertickets age out or get cleaned up on the SchedD side.\">#5336</a></span> <span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"/tickets?ticket=5337\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('5337'); return false;\" title=\"Have ubertickets age out or get cleaned up on the StartD side.\">#5337</a></span>  (By zmiller )</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">2015-Oct-23 20:35</td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon dot\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\"> \nCheck-in <span class=\"chng\"><a href=\"chngview?cn=46099\">[46099]</a></span>: On submit side, clear marks whenever new cred is stored. <span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"/tickets?ticket=5336\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('5336'); return false;\" title=\"Have ubertickets age out or get cleaned up on the SchedD side.\">#5336</a></span>  (By zmiller )</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">2015-Oct-23 20:24</td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon dot\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\"> \nCheck-in <span class=\"chng\"><a href=\"chngview?cn=46098\">[46098]</a></span>: Add a timer for sweeping the SEC_CREDENTIAL_DIRECTORY in the CredD <span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"/tickets?ticket=5336\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('5336'); return false;\" title=\"Have ubertickets age out or get cleaned up on the SchedD side.\">#5336</a></span>  (By zmiller )</td></tr>\n</tbody></table>", "type": "enhance", "last_change": "2016-Apr-26 20:52", "status": "resolved", "created": "2015-Oct-22 16:51", "fixed_version": "2015-Oct-22 16:51", "broken_version": "", "priority": "1", "subsystem": "Security", "assigned_to": "zmiller", "derived_from": "#5272", "creator": "zmiller", "rust": "", "customer_group": "cern", "visibility": "public", "notify": "zmiller@cs.wisc.edu, tannenba@cs.wisc.edu", "due_date": "20151029"}